{"tid":2226844,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"JPAC會議中討論日本COVER公司向中國網民道歉問題","createTime":"2020-10-02T09:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T12:32:21.000Z","uid":56115,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"98a4200457dea313a2fd08b60e8aa51ab7eff985","tid":2226844,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T09:52:27.000Z","msg":"由日本跨黨派議員組成的「日本對華政策國會議員聯盟」於較早時間舉行會議，會議上由平野小姐有份推動其中一個討論主題，VTuber「赤井はあと（赤井心）」以及「桐生ココ（桐生可可）」因為在直播上提及「台灣」而遭到官方下令禁止活動一事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N9QMR9q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN9QMR9q.jpg&h=bafb0217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJPAC的會員組成絕大多數皆為反中派人士，對於台灣及香港的人權相關議題相當關注。而此次VTuber遭到中國小粉紅咬定台獨的事件，自然成為了眾議員的關注焦點。<br />\n<br />\n其中，母公司日本COVER株式會社的道歉聲明及今後方針可說是為人詬病，沒有任何一個國家的網友及粉絲接受。如今已經引起了部分跨黨派議員的注意。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/giX0cdt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgiX0cdt.jpg&h=3490d6d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJPAC與IPAC（@ipacglobal)於昨日舉行會議，內容提及香港的最新情況，並設立關注香港自治小組，會議中討論了其他主要國對中的經濟和安全政策、以及提到一些受到中國困擾的國家的情況等。<br />\n我們邀請了以下專家提供資訊<br />\n井形彬先生（@AkiraIgata）、楊海英先生（@DcZ2sppUAxLS3nO<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家幫手retweet/like嘅內容<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/suzutaro26/status/1311539577979457536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsuzutaro26%2Fstatus%2F1311539577979457536&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdAh0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=f5a974a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsuzutaro26%2Fstatus%2F1311539577979457536&h=6899b7ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/suzutaro26/status/1311539577979457536</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Japan_pac/status/1311838061987196928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJapan_pac%2Fstatus%2F1311838061987196928&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdAh0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=e9a5b371\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJapan_pac%2Fstatus%2F1311838061987196928&h=5f17b027\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Japan_pac/status/1311838061987196928</a>"},{"pid":"cb9f85f474adbaba13b8692f0f9af7a5ce2461c8","tid":2226844,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T09:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b121944f2e79667881b6dfeea0031f223408079","tid":2226844,"uid":55599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T09:55:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3ec1bcb781489a9f44386d75ee8d53676e708c81","tid":2226844,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T09:56:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e1756c899908ae6ccf492b51e943b4070cabe4","tid":2226844,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T10:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8cfac90bf868c28090cd00f472f52310f041213","tid":2226844,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T10:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0967a8a274700c730d4e02022961453d3979d05e","tid":2226844,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T10:09:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd28060179f030345e62d9816dc90f42fe71a84","tid":2226844,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T10:16:2